<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$xi-yuan-si-shi-jie-65" href="/people/xi-yuan-si-shi-jie-65">西园寺世界</a>，<strong title="读书太少。" class="zu-question-my-bio">读书太少。</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="5">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$fang-ming-jun-76" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/fang-ming-jun-76" class="zg-link" title="方明俊">方明俊</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$da-zhen-tou-44" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/da-zhen-tou-44" class="zg-link" title="大枕头">大枕头</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wang-shi-zui" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wang-shi-zui" class="zg-link" title="王诗醉">王诗醉</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3240019" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">要歪一下题。<br>现在关于王思聪....哦，不对，王司徒的鬼畜，大部分往粗鄙之语的方向走，十分无聊。真正体现古人对喷智慧的，应该是这个（用k神找到的，懒得找了thank you  sir):这是你们要的合唱版《孔明&amp;王朗》<br><a href="http://www.bilibili.com/video/av982443/" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span class="invisible">http://www.</span><span class="visible">bilibili.com/video/av98</span><span class="invisible">2443/</span><span class="ellipsis"></span><i class="icon-external"></i></a><br>关注了很久的王司徒系列，印象中之前因为上面这个火了一把，然后也有几个up主做出了有意思的鬼畜，有几个粗鄙之语，但比较少。消声匿迹一段时间，最近又火了，我不知道是为什么，而且这次几乎都是粗鄙之语......你们就这么喜欢黑丞相吗？我从未见过如此厚颜无耻....【住口！】
<a href="/question/27642780/answer/37474410" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
<div class="fixed-summary-mask"></div>
</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
